#: includes/Admin.php:376
msgid ""
"The B2Brouter plugin allows you to automatically generate and send "
"electronic invoices for your WooCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"El plugin B2Brouter le permite generar y enviar automáticamente facturas "
"electrónicas para sus pedidos de WooCommerce."

#: includes/Admin.php:386
msgid "Next Steps"
msgstr "Próximos pasos"

#: includes/Admin.php:387
msgid "Step 1 — Get your B2Brouter credentials"
msgstr "Paso 1 — Obtén tus credenciales de B2Brouter"

#: includes/Admin.php:389
msgid "Register at app.b2brouter.net"
msgstr "Regístrate en app.b2brouter.net"

#: includes/Admin.php:390
msgid "Purchase an eDocExchange subscription."
msgstr "Contrata una suscripción eDocExchange."

#: includes/Admin.php:390
msgid "First month is for free!"
msgstr "¡El primer mes es gratis!"

#: includes/Admin.php:391
msgid "Go to Developers → API Keys in your B2Brouter dashboard."
msgstr "Vaya a Desarrolladores → Claves API en su panel de B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:392
msgid "Copy the API key and store it safely."
msgstr "Copie la clave API y guárdela de forma segura."

#: includes/Admin.php:394
msgid "Step 2 — Configure the plugin"
msgstr "Paso 2 — Configura el plugin"

#: includes/Admin.php:396
msgid "In WordPress, go to Invoices → Settings."
msgstr "En WordPress, vaya a Facturas → Configuración."

#: includes/Admin.php:397
msgid "Paste your B2Brouter API key."
msgstr "Pegue su clave API de B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:398
msgid ""
"Click Validate Key. If the key is correct, the plugin will display your "
"account information."
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en Validar clave. Si la clave es correcta, el plugin mostrará la "
"información de su cuenta."

#: includes/Admin.php:402
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Requisitos"

#: includes/Admin.php:404
msgid "A B2Brouter account with an active eDocExchange subscription"
msgstr "Una cuenta de B2Brouter con una suscripción activa a eDocExchange"

#: includes/Admin.php:405
msgid "WordPress 5.8 or higher"
msgstr "WordPress 5.8 o superior"

#: includes/Admin.php:406
msgid "WooCommerce 5.0 or higher, installed and active"
msgstr "WooCommerce 5.0 o superior, instalado y activo"

#: includes/Admin.php:407
msgid "PHP 7.4 or higher"
msgstr "PHP 7.4 o superior"

#: includes/Admin.php:414
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Cómo funciona"

#: includes/Admin.php:416
msgid ""
"Advanced configuration (transports, formats, taxes) is done in your "
"B2Brouter account."
msgstr ""
"La configuración avanzada (transportes, formatos, impuestos) se realiza en "
"tu cuenta de B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:417
msgid ""
"When an order is completed, the plugin automatically generates the invoice "
"via the B2Brouter API."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un pedido se completa, el plugin genera automáticamente la factura a "
"través de la API de B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:418
msgid ""
"B2Brouter sends the invoice to your customer using your configured transport "
"(email, Peppol, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"B2Brouter envía la factura a tu cliente usando el transporte configurado "
"(email, Peppol, etc.)."

#: includes/Admin.php:419
msgid ""
"Your customers can also download their invoices from their account page."
msgstr ""
"Tus clientes también pueden descargar sus facturas desde su página de cuenta."

#: includes/Admin.php:420
msgid "Credit notes are generated automatically when you process a refund."
msgstr ""
"Las facturas rectificativas se generan automáticamente cuando procesas un "
"reembolso."

#: includes/Admin.php:422
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "¿Listo para empezar?"

#: includes/Admin.php:425
msgid "Go to B2Brouter - Activate Subscription"
msgstr "Ir a B2Brouter - Activar suscripción"

#: includes/Admin.php:428
msgid "Configure Plugin"
msgstr "Configurar plugin"

#: includes/Admin.php:433
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Ventajas"

#: includes/Admin.php:435
msgid "Legal Compliance"
msgstr "Cumplimiento legal"

#: includes/Admin.php:435
msgid ""
"Automatic compliance with electronic invoicing regulations across multiple "
"countries."
msgstr ""
"Cumplimiento automático con las normativas de facturación electrónica en "
"múltiples países."

#: includes/Admin.php:436
msgid "Time Saving"
msgstr "Ahorro de tiempo"

#: includes/Admin.php:436
msgid ""
"Automatic generation of electronic invoices without manual intervention."
msgstr ""
"Generación automática de facturas electrónicas sin intervención manual."

#: includes/Admin.php:437
msgid "Professionalism"
msgstr "Profesionalidad"

#: includes/Admin.php:437
msgid "Invoices in standard formats: UBL, CII, XML, etc."
msgstr "Facturas en formatos estándar: UBL, CII, XML, etc."

#: includes/Admin.php:438
msgid "Cross-border"
msgstr "Transfronterizo"

#: includes/Admin.php:438
msgid "Support for international B2B and B2C transactions."
msgstr "Soporte para transacciones internacionales B2B y B2C."

#: includes/Admin.php:439
msgid "Full Integration"
msgstr "Integración completa"

#: includes/Admin.php:439
msgid "Works seamlessly with WooCommerce without affecting your workflow."
msgstr ""
"Funciona perfectamente con WooCommerce sin afectar tu flujo de trabajo."

#: includes/Admin.php:447
msgid "Need Help?"
msgstr "¿Necesita ayuda?"

#: includes/Admin.php:448
msgid ""
"Visit our GitHub repository for detailed documentation. If you need help, "
"please open an issue."
msgstr ""
"Visite nuestro repositorio de GitHub para consultar la documentación "
"detallada. Si necesita ayuda, abra un issue."

#: includes/Admin.php:450
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Documentación"

#: includes/Admin.php:451
msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "Registro de cambios"

#: includes/Admin.php:452
msgid "Support"
msgstr "Soporte"

#: includes/Admin.php:516
msgid "Webhook secret is required when webhooks are enabled."
msgstr ""
"El secreto del webhook es obligatorio cuando los webhooks están habilitados."

#: includes/Admin.php:589
msgid "Settings saved successfully."
msgstr "Configuración guardada correctamente."

#: includes/Admin.php:594
msgid "Invoice Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de facturas"

#: includes/Admin.php:599
msgid "API key is not configured. Please enter your B2Brouter API key below."
msgstr ""
"La clave API no está configurada. Introduzca su clave API de B2Brouter a "
"continuación."

#: includes/Admin.php:600 includes/Admin.php:646
msgid "Get your API key"
msgstr "Obtenga su clave API"

#: includes/Admin.php:611
msgid "API Key"
msgstr "Clave API"

#: includes/Admin.php:619
msgid "Enter your B2Brouter API key"
msgstr "Introduzca su clave API de B2Brouter"

#: includes/Admin.php:627
msgid "Use this account"
msgstr "Usar esta cuenta"

#: includes/Admin.php:639
msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "Desconocido"

#: includes/Admin.php:645
msgid "Enter your B2Brouter API key to enable invoice generation."
msgstr ""
"Introduzca su clave API de B2Brouter para habilitar la generación de "
"facturas."

#: includes/Admin.php:653
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "Entorno"

#: includes/Admin.php:662
msgid "Staging"
msgstr "Pruebas"

#: includes/Admin.php:665
msgid "Use staging environment for testing"
msgstr "Usar el entorno de pruebas para tests"

#: includes/Admin.php:672
msgid "Production"
msgstr "Producción"

#: includes/Admin.php:675
msgid "Use production environment for live invoices"
msgstr "Usar el entorno de producción para facturas reales"

#: includes/Admin.php:682
msgid "Invoice Generation Mode"
msgstr "Modo de generación de facturas"

#: includes/Admin.php:691
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "Automático"

#: includes/Admin.php:693
msgid "Generate invoice automatically when order is completed"
msgstr "Generar factura automáticamente cuando se complete el pedido"

#: includes/Admin.php:700
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "Manual"

#: includes/Admin.php:702
msgid "Generate invoice manually using a button in the order admin"
msgstr ""
"Generar factura manualmente usando un botón en la administración del pedido"

#: includes/Admin.php:708
msgid "Webhook Configuration"
msgstr "Configuración de webhooks"

#: includes/Admin.php:713
msgid "Enable Webhooks"
msgstr "Habilitar webhooks"

#: includes/Admin.php:723
msgid "Receive real-time invoice status updates from B2Brouter (recommended)."
msgstr ""
"Recibir actualizaciones de estado de facturas en tiempo real desde B2Brouter "
"(recomendado)."

#: includes/Admin.php:731
msgid "Webhook URL"
msgstr "URL del webhook"

#: includes/Admin.php:744
msgid "Copied!"
msgstr "¡Copiado!"

#: includes/Admin.php:744 includes/Admin.php:745
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Copiar"

#: includes/Admin.php:748
msgid "Enter this URL in your B2Brouter dashboard webhook settings."
msgstr ""
"Introduzca esta URL en la configuración de webhooks de su panel de B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:756
msgid "Webhook Secret"
msgstr "Secreto del webhook"

#: includes/Admin.php:766
msgid ""
"Enter the webhook secret from your B2Brouter dashboard to verify webhook "
"authenticity."
msgstr ""
"Introduzca el secreto del webhook desde su panel de B2Brouter para verificar "
"la autenticidad del webhook."

#: includes/Admin.php:774
msgid "Fallback Polling"
msgstr "Sondeo de respaldo"

#: includes/Admin.php:784
msgid ""
"Keep polling as backup (checks every 6 hours if webhook fails). Recommended "
"for reliability."
msgstr ""
"Mantener el sondeo como respaldo (verifica cada 6 horas si el webhook "
"falla). Recomendado para fiabilidad."

#: includes/Admin.php:790
msgid "Invoice Numbering & Series"
msgstr "Numeración y series de facturas"

#: includes/Admin.php:794
msgid "Invoice Series Code"
msgstr "Código de serie de factura"

#: includes/Admin.php:802
msgid "e.g., INV, S01"
msgstr "p. ej., FAC, S01"

#: includes/Admin.php:804
msgid ""
"Define one invoice series code for all invoices. B2Brouter allows one series "
"per invoice type. Leave empty to use B2Brouter default."
msgstr ""
"Defina un código de serie para todas las facturas. B2Brouter permite una "
"serie por tipo de factura. Déjelo vacío para usar el valor predeterminado de "
"B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:811
msgid "Credit Note Series Code"
msgstr "Código de serie de factura rectificativa"

#: includes/Admin.php:819
msgid "e.g., CN, R01"
msgstr "p. ej., NC, R01"

#: includes/Admin.php:821
msgid ""
"Define one credit note series code for all credit notes. B2Brouter allows "
"one series per type. Leave empty to use the same series as invoices."
msgstr ""
"Defina un código de serie para todas las facturas rectificativas. B2Brouter "
"permite una serie por tipo. Déjelo vacío para usar la misma serie que las "
"facturas."

#: includes/Admin.php:828
msgid "Invoice Numbering Pattern"
msgstr "Patrón de numeración de facturas"

#: includes/Admin.php:837
msgid "Automatic (B2Brouter manages numbering)"
msgstr "Automático (B2Brouter gestiona la numeración)"

#: includes/Admin.php:839
msgid "Let B2Brouter automatically assign invoice numbers"
msgstr "Dejar que B2Brouter asigne automáticamente los números de factura"

#: includes/Admin.php:846
msgid "WooCommerce Order Number"
msgstr "Número de pedido de WooCommerce"

#: includes/Admin.php:848
msgid "Use the WooCommerce order number as the invoice number"
msgstr "Usar el número de pedido de WooCommerce como número de factura"

#: includes/Admin.php:855
msgid "Sequential (plugin-managed)"
msgstr "Secuencial (gestionado por el plugin)"

#: includes/Admin.php:857
msgid "Plugin maintains sequential numbering per series (starts at 1)"
msgstr "El plugin mantiene una numeración secuencial por serie (empieza en 1)"

#: includes/Admin.php:864
msgid "Custom Pattern"
msgstr "Patrón personalizado"

#: includes/Admin.php:874
msgid ""
"Available placeholders: {order_id}, {order_number}, {year}, {month}, {day}. "
"Note: Series code is defined separately above and will be prefixed "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Marcadores disponibles: {order_id}, {order_number}, {year}, {month}, {day}. "
"Nota: El código de serie se define por separado arriba y se añadirá "
"automáticamente como prefijo."

#: includes/Admin.php:881
msgid "PDF Options"
msgstr "Opciones de PDF"

#: includes/Admin.php:885
msgid "Automatic PDF Caching"
msgstr "Caché automática de PDF"

#: includes/Admin.php:894
msgid "Automatically download and cache PDF when invoice is generated"
msgstr ""
"Descargar y almacenar en caché automáticamente el PDF cuando se genere la "
"factura"

#: includes/Admin.php:897
msgid ""
"When enabled, PDFs will be automatically downloaded from B2Brouter and "
"stored locally when an invoice is generated. This improves performance and "
"reduces API calls."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está habilitado, los PDFs se descargarán automáticamente de B2Brouter "
"y se almacenarán localmente cuando se genere una factura. Esto mejora el "
"rendimiento y reduce las llamadas a la API."

#: includes/Admin.php:905
msgid "PDF Storage Location"
msgstr "Ubicación de almacenamiento de PDF"

#: includes/Admin.php:910
msgid ""
"Invoice PDFs are stored in this directory. Files are protected from direct "
"access via .htaccess rules."
msgstr ""
"Los PDFs de facturas se almacenan en este directorio. Los archivos están "
"protegidos contra el acceso directo mediante reglas .htaccess."

#: includes/Admin.php:928
#, php-format
msgid "Currently storing %d PDF(s) using %s of disk space"
msgstr "Actualmente almacenando %d PDF(s) usando %s de espacio en disco"

#: includes/Admin.php:937
msgid "Directory will be created automatically when first PDF is downloaded"
msgstr ""
"El directorio se creará automáticamente cuando se descargue el primer PDF"

#: includes/Admin.php:945
msgid "Email PDF Attachments"
msgstr "Adjuntar PDF en correos electrónicos"

#: includes/Admin.php:954
msgid "Attach PDF to Order Completed email (sent to customer)"
msgstr "Adjuntar PDF al correo de pedido completado (enviado al cliente)"

#: includes/Admin.php:962
msgid "Attach PDF to Customer Invoice email"
msgstr "Adjuntar PDF al correo de factura del cliente"

#: includes/Admin.php:970
msgid "Attach PDF to Refunded Order email (credit note/rectificative)"
msgstr "Adjuntar PDF al correo de pedido reembolsado (factura rectificativa)"

#: includes/Admin.php:973
msgid ""
"Automatically attach invoice PDFs to customer emails. \"Order Completed\" is "
"sent when orders are fulfilled. \"Customer Invoice\" is sent for pending/"
"unpaid orders or when manually sent from admin panel. \"Refunded Order\" is "
"sent when orders are refunded."
msgstr ""
"Adjuntar automáticamente PDFs de facturas a los correos del cliente. "
"\"Pedido completado\" se envía cuando se completan los pedidos. \"Factura "
"del cliente\" se envía para pedidos pendientes/impagados o cuando se envía "
"manualmente desde el panel de administración. \"Pedido reembolsado\" se "
"envía cuando se reembolsan los pedidos."

#: includes/Admin.php:981
msgid "Automatic Cleanup"
msgstr "Limpieza automática"

#: includes/Admin.php:990
msgid "Automatically delete old cached PDFs"
msgstr "Eliminar automáticamente los PDFs en caché antiguos"

#: includes/Admin.php:994
msgid "Delete PDFs older than"
msgstr "Eliminar PDFs con más de"

#: includes/Admin.php:1001
msgid "days"
msgstr "días"

#: includes/Admin.php:1004
msgid ""
"When enabled, PDFs older than the specified number of days will be "
"automatically deleted daily via cron job. This helps manage disk space usage."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está habilitado, los PDFs con más días de los especificados se "
"eliminarán automáticamente diariamente mediante una tarea cron. Esto ayuda a "
"gestionar el uso del espacio en disco."

